In my remaster, the text parser is replaced with a local LLM Llama 3.1, enabling richer, dynamic interactions and reasoning for next actions. The original 4-color graphics are now 1080p animated visuals, created with DALLÂ·E 3 and RunwayML, with added cutscenes, ambient sounds, and music.

This project is my tribute to the original creators, and I hope youâ€™ll enjoy rediscovering this classic as much as I did bringing it back to life!"

